dcterms:description: HVAC usage data collected from a university campus’s energy data repository, including air flow (actual and setpoints), cooling and heating setpoints, damper position command, discharge temperature, HW valve command, actual space temperature, and occupancy status with a timestamp. The data were collected every minute from 7/9/2019 to 2/1/2020.
dcterms:title: HVAC usage data

dcterms:description: Energy data from a university campus’s energy data repository, used for predictive modeling of occupancy patterns and HVAC control.
dcterms:title: Energy data from university campus
